{
  "stem": "13141.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm going to use the bathroom real quick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there's one--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--item I forgot to mention.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hitler came to Stuttgart on his birthday, on his 50th birthday, which was April 20th, 1940.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since he went to the Rathaus in Stuttgart-- which is the, the, the town hall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my grandmother's home-- house, was right on the Marktplatz, on the main square, where I stayed with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the, the houses on the Marktplatz had to be [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] fixed with flowers and bouquets and the, the swastika flag.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Since we, of course, didn't have a swastika flag and we, we, [LAUGHS] we just didn't see any sense of going through these motions, we actually were contacted already a few days before by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Someone came to our home, to Marktplatz 19.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Number 19 was the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they told us that Hitler was coming and that, that they would send us a couple of people to take care of the-- all the flower trimmings and the swastika flag, which was hung out of the house, because it was hung out of all the other houses, and that we, we could not look out of the window or leave the house after 8 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We should stay inside until in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hitler came actually around 12:00.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we were not supposed to look out of the window, which we didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were two Gestapo officers who came to our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One was on the roof, and the other one was inside with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
